text: Practically brand new haven nestled in the Shelter Bay community! This home boasts an inviting open-concept layout with vaulted ceilings and expansive windows bathing the space in natural light with large slider to backyard deck. Plus easy-to-maintain vinyl plank flooring. Enjoy cozy evenings by the chic electric fireplace, and entertain effortlessly in the fresh white kitchen featuring a walk-in pantry, quartz counters & spacious eat-at island. Retreat to the primary bedroom with its adjoining 3/4 bath featuring a floor-to-ceiling tile shower and walk-in closet. Another bedroom and full bath offer flexibility and convenience. With a 2-car garage and a charming yard awaiting your landscaping touch, this home is ready to fulfill your dreams.
Ready to build your dream home in the heart of Burlington. all utilities available to property.make Your dreams come true

You won't want to miss this well-maintained 3-bed, 1-bath home in town. Recent upgrades include new roof, fresh paint, new windows, and updated bathroom. The large 23x35 shop provides ample space for hobbies or storage. The flat lot makes for a great gardening and entertaining space. Enjoy the rhubarb, strawberry, raspberry plants and plum tree. Convenient location close to schools and dining. Easy highway access.
Beautiful wooded 2.5 acres just across the road from the Sauk River for recreational use or to build a dream home. Boat launch just down the road.

Indulge in the allure of this captivating residence boasting breathtaking vistas of Mt. Baker and Padilla Bay. Immerse yourself in elegance with 10' ceilings, adorned with architectural cove crown molding and baseboards. Revel in the opulence of oak, travertine, and heated slate flooring, while double-sided fireplaces add warmth and charm. Work or unwind in the dedicated office, offering French doors leading to a charming courtyard. Retreat to the primary bedroom, featuring a luxurious ensuite with a soaking tub and walk-in shower. Delight in outdoor living with courtyards, decks, and patios, all within reach of the trailhead to Cranberry Lake. Experience luxury living at its finest in this remarkable abode. Washers & dryers on both levels

This single story home blends modern luxury with classic charm featuring all the contemporary amenities you desire in a new home. The open-concept layout with plenty of natural light enhances the spacious feel, creating a perfect setting for both comfortable living & entertaining. The kitchen boasts top-of-the-line appliances, granite countertops & storage. The allure doesn't end indoors step outside into your private oasis. The professionally landscaped yard is a masterpiece, showcasing a manicured lawn, and an array of textures plus a covered deck. A brand-new swim spa that beckons you to indulge in relaxation and fitness year-round. This high-end addition elevates your outdoor living offering a perfect blend of luxury and wellness.

Absolutely darling, this charming and super affordable cottage-style home is just a short distance from downtown Sedro shops and eateries. With a greatroom-style floorplan, this home features a large primary bedroom, 2nd bedroom, and one full bath. The kitchen is a highlight with its eating bar, new paint, ample counter space, built-in pantry, and classic Dutch door. Situated on a spacious corner lot that's drenched in sunshine, there's plenty of room for RV/Boat parking. The detached garage, with its new roof and extra storage room, adds further value. The home has new gutters.Enjoy the impressive garden space and a fantastic catio or window box, perfect for herbs and plants. Close to schools, parks, and I-5, this home is not to be missed!

Welcome home to this tidy, well maintained one level home boasting 4 bedrooms. Upon arrival you'll be taken in by the fantastic curb appeal and a warm, inviting atmosphere. It offers an efficient kitchen, living room with cozy gas fireplace, and lovely dining area which looks out at the spacious fenced back yard. Plant a garden, enjoy hosting summer gatherings or just relax on the patio. Outdoor adventures are beckoning you to explore the community forest land trails, just 2 blocks away, leading to nearby Little Cranberry Lake. Close to parks and schools. Single car garage plus RV parking. This home offers a perfect blend of comfort, convenience and tranquility. Easy commute to NAS Whidbey. Don't miss the opportunity to make this your own!

This 4-bedroom home is a must see! Located in beautiful Skagit Valley, sitting on a newly fenced .3-acre corner lot with a view of the lowlands and Cascade mountains. This spacious 4-level home is close to golfing, shopping, dining, entertainment and walking trails. Features: 4 Bd, 2.5 Baths, detached 2-car garage, shop/exercise room, RV parking, on-demand hot water heater, newer gas furnace, remodeled master bath, 3 driveways w/parking for 6-10, open dining room, woodstove, vaulted ceilings, fully enclosed side room w/view, large back deck, fully fenced back yards, fenced garden, new 8' x 10' greenhouse, fruit trees include rainier cherry, peach, apple, and plum, also raspberries, blueberries, kiwi and more!

Experience the serenity of country living right outside city limits! This immaculate 3-bed, 3-bath home is privately nestled on almost 1 acre in a secluded cul-de-sac. With many recent updates this home combines style, comfort, & luxury. It feels like home with an inviting entryway, flowing floor plan, high ceilings & spacious rooms. This smart home is adorned with gleaming natural light, flexible spaces & lots of storage. The primary suite is desirably located on the main level and presents its own private deck! Enjoy the expansive kitchen with island, granite countertops & large deck overlooking the mesmerizing backyard oasis. Outside you'll find a manicured yard w/ a garden, flowering trees & plants, pond, & the most charming greenhouse!

Unlock the door to your dream home with this expansive 1.4-acre property, offering the ideal canvas for your architectural aspirations. Nestled in a tranquil setting, graced by a picturesque seasonal creek and lush with timber, this plot ensures privacy and natural beauty. Water access is conveniently available through a cistern system or can be sourced from Fruitdale Rd, a mere 500 feet away. Power readily established on-site. Experience the liberty of expansive space - clear the land to suit your vision while preserving the natural environment. Enjoy the freedom of no HOA constraints and let your creativity reign supreme. Your perfect home awaits!

Single-story 3 bedroom home conveniently located in the heart of Mount Vernon. Step inside to discover beautiful wood flooring in the living area along with built in shelves and fireplace. This open-concept layout allows lots of natural light into the dining area and the kitchen. Entertain on the inviting deck. The partially fenced yard provides privacy while still allowing ample space for outdoor activities, surrounded by beautiful landscaping. Single car garage provides parking and storage along with extra gravel parking on the side. Easy access to I5, schools, parks, hospital and amenities.

Welcome home to this charming gem in the heart of Sedro-Woolley! Completely renovated from the studs out in 2020, this delightful house has modern upgrades & stylish finishes throughout. Step inside to discover ductless heat pumps providing efficient heating & cooling, for year-round comfort. The laminate floors add a touch of elegance, complementing the new roof, windows, and woodwork. Enjoy the convenience of an added half bath, ideal for guests and everyday use. The new kitchen features sleek countertops, contemporary cabinetry, and quality appliances. Situated on a large lot, there's ample space for gardening enthusiasts or the opportunity to add a garage or workshop. This turnkey property is ready to welcome you home.

This charming home, originally built in 1920, has been beautifully remodeled, blending vintage charm w/modern amenities. Step inside to discover the warmth of the original fir floors, reminding you of the home's heritage. Main house features 3 bedrooms & 1 bathroom, offering comfortable living spaces that are both inviting & functional. Modern appliances & stylish finishes, this kitchen is sure to impress. Outside, you'll find a delightful surprise - a tiny house ADU in the BY. This studio-style ADU provides a versatile space that can be used as a guest suite or rental opportunity. Windows & roof were replaced during the full remodel 6 years ago. Don't miss the opportunity to own this unique blend of historic charm & modern convenience.

Welcome to your spacious retreat! This charming rambler offers over 2000 sq ft of modern living space on over 1/3 acre, backing onto a serene green belt. Freshly painted interiors and a new roof greet you inside. Enjoy seamless entertaining in the well-appointed kitchen and relax in the tranquil master suite with its attached spa-like bathroom. Additional upgrades include a new AC heat pump for year-round comfort. Outside, the expansive yard is perfect for outdoor activities and includes a hot tub for everyday relaxation. Conveniently located near amenities, this home offers both comfort and convenience. Don't miss out on this modern living experience!

Entertain and enjoy mountain views from this spacious, window-filled Skagit Highlands home. The beautiful formal living room welcomes you with a cozy gas fireplace and plenty of room for friends. Open kitchen with bamboo floors, walk-in pantry, stainless steel appliances, and eating bar flows into the inviting dining room that provides plenty of room to gather and mingle. Upstairs enjoy the large, light-filled family room, primary bedroom with spacious bathroom that includes a soaking tub, large tile surround shower, and walk-in closet, plus good sized second and third bedrooms. Outside, enjoy the covered front porch, low maintenance yard, landscaping, and cozy patio.

Enjoy country living just minutes from town. This 1966 Tri-Level home checks all the boxes. Just shy of an acre, quiet backyard with plenty of room for outdoor entertainment. Close to town but feels miles away. Come see for yourself all of the possibilities.

This newly remodeled 3 bedroom, .75 bath home offers modern comfort at an affordable price. All new kitchen, appliances, windows, and flooring. Easy highway access and conveniently located near stores. With updated interiors, new appliances, and a convenient location, it's the perfect blend of style and affordability. Don't miss out on this fantastic opportunity to call this home yours!

Almost 57 acres with marketable timber. This ultra-private acreage sits high above the valley. Hunter/campers paradise. 2.2 acres ready for your off grid cabin. Access to the property is about a 2 mile hike in. No services. Get away from it all. The possibilities are endless, off grid living or hold for investment. Elk, deer, and wildlife all abundant. Truly a paradise.

North Hill new construction! Daylight rambler with basement design and all the modern qualities and finishes. Main floor living with all you need! Great layout with first floor entry to Living Room, Kitchen, Dining, Primary with Ensuite, Utility and 2 car attached garage. Natural Gas fireplace and open concept. Fully finished, daylight lower level with Family room, 2 guest Bedrooms, Full Bath and loads of storage throughout! Enjoy gorgeous sunsets on your main floor deck or lower level patio. The Olympic Mountains, Skagit Valley and Skagit River backdrop are the perfect setting for these beautiful new home. Conveniently located to shopping, schools, parks and the I-5 corridor for commuting.

This lovely home was completely remodeled in 2020 adding modern touches throughout! Inside discover 3 bedrooms, 1.75 bath. Kitchen has SS appliances & butcher block countertops combining style & functionality. Entertain or unwind & enjoy the ambiance of an electric fireplace insert in the spacious living room. Mudroom at back entrance adds convenience & basement offers extra storage. Outside you'll find an expansive yard w/ endless possibilities for outdoor enjoyment, ample parking, detached 1-car garage & a 2-bay shop providing workspace options and more storage. Perfect for commuters, this home is close in proximity to Janicki Industries & Seattle City Light. Don't miss your chance to experience small-town living in the Pacific Northwest!

Effort-free living in desirable Creekside Village. This 2 bedroom, 1 bath home with recent updates feels like a custom home inside. Vaulted ceilings and skylights brighten the space, and a cozy gas fireplace warms the living and dining rooms. The updated kitchen has quartz countertops, stainless steel appliances and lots of storage. The primary bedroom suite is oversized with an updated ensuite bathroom. Large 2-car garage for parking and storage. Rest easy; the HOA handles exterior maintenance and landscaping in this peaceful setting. Ideal location near the Senior Center and community pool. Just minutes from Island Hospital, shopping, restaurants, and parks. Creekside also offers RV and boat storage for a nominal fee.

This legacy home lies within a category of properties rarely available, sited in Mount Vernon's desirable community, The Hill. Crafted by Elden Pollock, the visionary for the Lincoln Theatre, this bespoke residence exudes architectural mastery. Enjoy panoramic vistas of the valley, river, and downtown Mount Vernon. Step into Colonial elegance with white oak floors and 1940s craftsman doors adorned with crystal knobs. Entertain in the living room, graced by a fireplace and French doors to a sun-soaked patio. The kitchen, a sanctuary of culinary creativity, boasts an inviting nook and buffet. Dine beneath a sparkling chandelier then retreat to the primary bedroom with an ensuite bath. Nearby walking trails lead to town and the river's edge.

Rare opportunity to own a FEE SIMPLE (no lease) custom-built rambler, boasting a great room concept. Step into a haven of tranquility with mature, landscaping, and enjoy a park-like ambiance, with a greenbelt backdrop and privacy offered by the fenced backyard. A deck and pergola offer a serene retreat where you can unwind and entertain. Home offers a free standing fireplace perfect for those crisp chilly days. Enjoy the PNW lifestyle with community activities such as golf, tennis courts, and a club house, providing endless opportunities for recreation and socializing. Explore the beauty of two private beaches and take advantage of the free boat ramp, enhancing your waterfront living experience.

Welcome to your riverside sanctuary on the picturesque Skagit River, where tranquility meets natural beauty on 1/2 acre. Nestled amidst towering trees and lush greenery, this charming home offers a peaceful retreat from the hustle and bustle of everyday life. Step inside to discover a cozy yet spacious interior, bathed in natural light streaming through large windows that frame breathtaking views of the river and surrounding landscape. The open-concept living area is perfect for both relaxing evenings by the fireplace and entertaining guests, with a seamless flow into the dining area and kitchen. Outside, the expansive deck beckons you to unwind and soak in the sights and sounds of nature. Perfect for a short term rental or a getaway home.

Impeccably maintained home on a generously sized, meticulously landscaped lot. Expansive single story four bedroom home in the desirable BayView area with an inviting open floorplan, spacious rooms & superb outdoor entertaining space. Enjoy the versatility of a large bonus room adorned with beamed vaulted ceilings & projector for entertainment. The spacious kitchen offers stunning mountain views, abundant counter space, stainless steel appliances, & a wall of pantry storage, seamlessly flowing into the dining & living areas. Additionally, a detached heated & insulated shop offers ample space for hobbies or storage. A ground-level 1 bedroom apartment featuring new kitchen, laundry room, & a bathroom with walk-in tile shower adds versatility.

Sought-after Big Lake property in Skagit Valley! Build your dream or vacation home on pristine 1.1 acres. Flat lower area is ready to welcome a shop to store your boat or RV. Open space for future parking or campsite. The upper land has been cleared and will provide a perfect new homesite w/ majestic views of Big Lake. PUD water & electricity on-site, sewer at the street. Septic design & critical areas survey completed. Great views of the mountains and Big Lake. Close to golf course, restaurants, corner store and boat launch. Easy access to Hwy 9. Short drive to Mt Vernon. Welcome home!

Experience adventure and tranquility in this charming 2-bed, 1 full-bath tiny home nestled in the picturesque Lake Cavanaugh community! Boasting 934 sq ft, this cozy home features many special touches throughout, offering the perfect retreat for both adventure seekers and relaxation enthusiasts. Snuggle up by the wood stove after a day of exploration or unwind in the serene garden space. With 2.5 acres to roam, including outbuildings and trails, every day brings discoveries. A 5 bedroom septic has already been installed. Cleared and ready to build your dream home. Public boat launch and the Cavanaugh Community Center are just a few minutes away. This unrestricted lake allows skiing. Easy drive from Seattle or Bellingham.

Custom built home & SHOP on the edge of town yet close to everything! Minutes to Little Mountain Park trails. This 3042 sqr ft home is well designed & beautiful throughout. Main floor living, A/C, 4 bdrms, 3.25 bthrms plus a large bonus space for hobbies or playroom. Kitchen, dining & living room w/ tons of natural light. Cathedral ceilings, picture windows and a gas frplc. Daylight basement can be used as the 4th bedroom or guest area. It has a kitchenette & bath w/ its own entrance. Easy care multi-level decking, park-like landscaping & mountain views! Fruit trees, garden space and flowers galore! The SHOP is approx 1000 sqr ft. wired w/ 200 amp service & a 50 amp RV hookup. Room for cars, RV and/ or boat plus a large loft. A must see!

Don't miss this opportunity! Imagine owning a 5-acre property in desirable Bow with stunning views of the Skagit Valley, Bay, & Islands! This property features a 3-bedroom rambler & a large shop/2-car garage. Set back from Colony Road, down a driveway lined with mature cedar trees, sits a 1995 time capsule. The house remains in its original condition, including the kitchen, bathrooms, carpets & exterior deck. Update the home as much or as little as you desire! The serene property gently slopes towards the view, showcasing magnificent original landscaping with blooming rhododendrons, fruit trees, & more. The unfinished basement, with exterior access, offers an opportunity to add square footage or create a rental suite/ AirBnB.
